=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Linux, Apache, MySQL, and PHP.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>c.<strong>MEAN Stack:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>MongoDB, Express, Angular, and Node.js.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>d.<strong>Ruby on Rails:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Ruby and Rails.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>e.<strong>Django:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Python and Django framework.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>f.<strong>Flask:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Python and Flask micro-framework.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>g.<strong>Meteor:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>A full-stack JavaScript framework.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing the right stack depends on project requirements, developer expertise, and specific use cases. Each stack comes with its own strengths and suitability for different types of applications.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"faq-what-are-the-alternatives-of-mern-stack\">FAQ- What Are The Alternatives Of MERN Stack?<\/h2>\n\n\n<div id=\"rank-math-faq\" class=\"rank-math-block\">\n<div class=\"rank-math-list \">\n<div id=\"faq-question-1701343739350\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q1. What should I do after MERN stack?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans.  MERN, Python with Django, and Ruby on Rails are all popular web development stacks with specific strengths. MERN, using JavaScript throughout, excels in scalability and real-time features, making it suitable for large projects. Python with Django emphasizes rapid development and versatility, catering to both simple and moderately complex applications. Ruby on Rails prioritizes convention over configuration, making it ideal for quick prototyping and smaller projects. The choice among these stacks depends on project requirements, team expertise, and development preferences.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1701343749377\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q2. Which is better .NET or MERN stack?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. The best choice will depend on your specific needs and preferences.\u00a0If you need a fast, easy-to-use, and scalable platform, then MEAN Stack will be the most preferrable choice. However, if you need a platform with more security features and support, PHP or . Net would be a better choice.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1701343763047\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h4 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q3. What is the alternative to MERN in 2023?<\/h4>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. The\u00a0<strong>PERN stack<\/strong>\u00a0works just like the  MERN but utilizes PostgreSQL. It is a more reliable, secure SQL-based database system, instead of MongoDB. The Ruby on Rails stack can provide developers to create an entire web application by combining Ruby on Rails with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, known for its security and simplicity<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The Alternatives Of MERN Stack When it comes to web development, the MERN Stack\u2014comprising MongoDB, Express, React, and Node.js\u2014stands as a popular and robust choice. However, the landscape offers a variety of alternatives, each bringing its own set of technologies and advantages to the table. Among these alternatives are the MEVN Stack with Vue.js, the &#8230; <a title=\"What Are The Alternatives Of MERN Stack?\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/what-are-the-alternatives-of-mern-stack\/\" aria-label=\"More on What Are The Alternatives Of MERN Stack?\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":4126,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[736],"tags":[749],"class_list":["post-4123","post","type-post","